// https://developer.apple.com/ios/human-interface-guidelines/visual-design/color/

const colors = {
  red: '#FF3B30',
  orange: '#FF9500',
  yellow: '#FFCC00',
  green: '#4CD964',
  tealBlue: '#5AC8FA',
  blue: '#007AFF',
  purple: '#5856D6',
  pink: '#FF2D55',

  white: '#FFFFFF',
  customGray: '#EFEFF4',
  lightGray: '#E5E5EA',
  lightGray2: '#D1D1D6',
  midGray: '#C7C7CC',
  gray: '#8E8E93',
  black: '#000000',
}

export default colors
